We use personality types to make online dating and finding friends more meaningful.   This works in 3 simple steps:  1. You fill out some basic information about yourself. 2. You take our personality test.  3. You get compatible matches to date or make friends!  Our personality test is inspired by the 16 personalities test, which uses psychometric testing to classify people into 16 personalities as follows:  INFP - The Idealist ENFP - The Inspirer INTJ - The Strategist ENTJ - The Commander INFJ - The Mystic ENFJ - The Protagonist INTP - The Thinker ENTP - The Visionary ISFP - The Adventurer ESFP - The Entertainer ISTP - The Craftsman ESTP - The Dynamo ISTJ - The Inspector ESTJ - The Executive ISFJ - The Nurturer ESFJ - The Guardian  The four letters in the 16 personalities above stand for the following:  E: Extrovert I: Introvert N: Intuitive S: Sensing T: Thinking F: Feeling P: Perceiving J: Judging  We are pioneering the application of the 16 personalities in the context of friend-finding and dating apps.  We are idealists, but we are also realists. We realize that looks have a role to play in dating apps, which is why profile pictures are shown on our users' profiles. However, we refuse to believe that looks are the most important factor for meaningful relationships to happen. Love is deep and tender and cannot be built on looks alone.  Our core philosophy is that personality is the foundation for dating, making friends, and any type of human relationship. If you feel the same way, then you will find yourself at home on our app.  Although Ur My Type was initially launched as a dating app, it can also be used to make friends. In fact, our data shows that up to 50% of our users are on the app primarily to find friends. So, whether you happen to be looking for an online dating site to get hit by cupid, or just feel a bit lonely and want to make new friends, just turn up and you are likely to find what you are looking for on Ur My Type.  At the moment, 65% of our users are introverts. There might be more extroverts than introverts in society and on most other dating apps, but on our app the opposite is true. It might be because people on our app are just really nice, as we often receive a lot of feedback that our users are kind, tender, and respectful, which creates a great environment for introverts.  Beyond personality types, our users also have a wide variety of interests:  72% of our users state anime as one of their interests. So if you are looking for an anime dating app, or just looking to meet new people who feel the same way about anime, then you have come to the right place.  71% of our users also identify as gamers. Hence, if you are searching for a gamer dating app or want to date other gamers, then there is a high chance for that to happen on our app.  65% of our users have an interest in enneagram. So if you are looking for an enneagram dating app, or just want to meet new people who are also interested in enneagram, then you can find what you are looking for on our app.  Finally, 50% of our user-base state that they are interested in astrology and zodiac signs. If you are looking for an astrology dating app, or want to date others who are into astrology and zodiac, then there is a good chance that it might happen on our online dating site.  We have also recently created a new feature called "My Type" inspired by the random chat format. Similar to random chat, a user clicks on a button that says "Find me my type" and is instantly connected to someone who is also online right now in less than 30 seconds! Unlike random chat, however, the matching is not random, but is based on our personality-driven algorithm.  Beyond playing cupid & matching people, the app also contains a dedicated community section in the form of an online forum where users can exchange ideas, post memes, and interact with each other in fun and meaningful ways.   The app is available worldwide.  https://www.urmytype.app/terms-and-conditions
